name: qvina
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "qvina" %}
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/hadim/qvina/archive/cmake.zip
  sha256: da78b5dc3d7a0b145f13ac7698bae02a9f03fdf10b5fbf06dadce459b3f73a66

build:
  skip: True  # [(win and vc<14)]
  number: 2

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - cmake >=3.12
    - make
  host:
    - boost-cpp
  run:
    - boost-cpp
  run_constrained:
    - __osx >={{ MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET|default("10.9") }}  # [osx]

test:
  commands:
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/vina  # [not win]
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/qvina2  # [not win]
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/qvinaw  # [not win]
    - vina --help  # [not win]
    - qvina2 --help  # [not win]
    - qvinaw --help  # [not win]

about:
  home: https://qvina.github.io/
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Accurately speed up AutoDock Vina'
  doc_url: https://qvina.github.io/
  dev_url: https://github.com/QVina/qvina

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hadim
smithy_version:
No azure token. Create a token and
put it in ~/.conda-smithy/azure.token
